## DeepKeys type

Get deep keys of T.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export type DeepKeys<T> = InternalDeepKeys<T>
```
<b>References:</b> [InternalDeepKeys](./types-kit.internaldeepkeys.md)

## Example


```ts
 interface Props {
      a?: {
        readonly b?: number
        c: {
          d?: number
        }
      }
      e: number
    }

 // Expect: 'a' | 'a.b' | 'a.c' | 'a.c.d' | 'e'
 type PropKeys = DeepKeys<Props>
```
